beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Barcelona and Copenhagen’s only two previous meetings came in the group stage of the 2010-11 UEFA Champions League – Barcelona won 2-0 in the home fixture thanks to a Lionel Messi brace, before drawing 1-1 in the reverse fixture in Denmark. beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Paris Saint-Germain vs Newcastle United - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: Paris Saint-Germain vs Newcastle United - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Paris SG and Newcastle’s only previous meetings came in the 2023-24 UEFA Champions League – the two sides drew their meeting at the Parc des Princes, after Eddie Howe’s side had won 4-1 in the first game at St. James’ Park. This will be Newcastle’s 10th away game against a French side in Europe, while they have only managed one victory from the previous nine : 4-0 v Sochaux in the UEFA Cup in November 2004.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
